MTN has unveiled its Black Friday Mega Deals which include big price cuts on its SIM-only 30GB MTN Sky package. MTN said its Black Friday Mega deals are available from 29 November to 2 December, and also include MTN Made For Me S, M, L, and XL specials. These deals will only be available on a 24-month contract and are subject to device and SIM availability, RICA registration, and successful credit vetting. “Pay as you go” deals and MTN Business deals are also available, it added. Additionally, free promotional value – YouTube and Anytime Data plus MTN-to-MTN minutes – is provisioned every month for the first 6 months of the contract offers. “The free promotional value – YouTube and Anytime Data plus MTN-to-MTN minutes – is provisioned every month for the first 6 months of the contract,” said MTN. “On month 7 the customer will be billed at an additional price to the price plan subscription. The customer has an option to cancel the Black Friday bundle at any time.” MTN stated certain deals are “never to be repeated”. MTN’s Black Friday 2019 deals can be seen below. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-330557" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MTN-4-scaled.jpg" alt="MTN" width="640" height="915" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MTN-4-scaled.jpg 1791w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MTN-4-280x400.jpg 280w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MTN-4-301x430.jpg 301w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MTN-4-768x1098.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MTN-4-1074x1536.jpg 1074w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MTN-4-1433x2048.jpg 1433w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MTN-4-1200x1715.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-330555" src="https:/